cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with zero-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed model involves deep learning techniques (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) to fuse multiple semantic modalities. The experiments are conducted on image datasets (cs.MM).
